sqlParams.paramVal: SELECT 'MAX_KEY' AS max_key, COALESCE(MAX(offering_type_key) , 0) FROM dim_offering_type

properties.propertyVal:
SELECT DISTINCT(SRC_offering_ods.OFFERING_TYPE) AS OFFERING_TYPE
	,'V4' AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MY_BOLD_ODS_OFFERING_ODS SRC_offering_ods 
WHERE SRC_offering_ods.OFFERING_PID IS NOT NULL
AND SRC_offering_ods.IS_CURRENT = 1

DI_CF(SRC_panel_ods.panel_pid IS NOT NULL AND 
SRC_panel_ods.is_current = 1 )

DI_CF(SRC_offering_ods.offering_pid IS NOT NULL
AND SRC_offering_ods.is_current = 1 )
DI_CF(SRC_vaccine_ods.vaccine_pid IS NOT NULL AND SRC_vaccine_ods.is_current = 1)
DI_CF(SRC_encounter_ods.encounter_pid IS NOT NULL AND SRC_encounter_ods.is_current = 1)
DI_CF(SRC_test_kit_ods.test_kit_pid IS NOT NULL AND SRC_test_kit_ods.is_current = 1)

attributes.attrExprVal:
CASE 
        WHEN SRC_offering_ods.TEST_KIT_PID IS NOT NULL THEN SRC_offering_ods.TEST_KIT_NAME 
        WHEN SRC_offering_ods.PANEL_PID IS NOT NULL THEN SRC_offering_ods.PANEL_NAME 
        WHEN SRC_offering_ods.VACCINE_PID IS NOT NULL THEN SRC_offering_ods.VACCINE_NAME 
        WHEN SRC_offering_ods.ENCOUNTER_PID IS NOT NULL THEN SRC_offering_ods.ENCOUNTER_NAME 
END

CASE 
        WHEN SRC_offering_ods.TEST_KIT_PID IS NOT NULL THEN SRC_test_kit_ods.TEST_KIT_DESC  
        WHEN SRC_offering_ods.PANEL_PID IS NOT NULL THEN SRC_offering_ods.PANEL_NAME 
        WHEN SRC_offering_ods.VACCINE_PID IS NOT NULL THEN SRC_vaccine_ods.VACCINE_DESC 
        WHEN SRC_offering_ods.ENCOUNTER_PID IS NOT NULL THEN SRC_encounter_ods.ENCOUNTER_DESC 
END
CASE WHEN SRC_dim_offering_type.OFFERING_TYPE_KEY IS NULL THEN -1 ELSE SRC_dim_offering_type.OFFERING_TYPE_KEY   END
